ARTICLE.TITLE: San Antonio police searching for suspect who robbed a H-E-B cashier
ARTICLE.TEXT:
San Antonio police are searching for a suspect who robbed a H-E-B cashier on Sunday.

The suspect entered the H-E-B at 8503 N.W. Military Hwy on the North Side at approximately 2:05 p.m.

The suspect walked up to the cashier and demanded money. Fearing for her safety, the cashier complied with the suspect's demands.

According to police, the suspect then ran out of the store, jumped into a vehicle, and fled the scene.

Crime Stoppers (210-224-7867) may pay up to $5,000 for information which leads to felony arrests in the robbery.
